Package: gpbiometrics
Type: Package
Title: Process and Report Gazepoint Biometrics Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Stefanos", family = "Balaskas", email = "s.balaskas@ac.upatras.gr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for importing, validating, quality-checking, preprocessing, summarising, synchronising, modelling, plotting, and reporting Gazepoint Biometrics exports. The package focuses on Gazepoint-specific biometric channels such as GSR/EDA, heart rate, interbeat intervals, pulse signal, engagement dial, TTL markers, and synchronisation fields that can be combined with Gazepoint GP3 and GP3 HD eye-tracking workflows.
